                        </a></div></div><ol class="sense_single" htag="ol"><li class="sense" hclass="sense" id="ashe_sng_1" htag="li"><span class="sensetop" hclass="sensetop" htag="span"><span class="def" htag="span" hclass="def">(1943-93) a US tennis player. He was the first African American to win the <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/the-us-open#the_us_open_topg_1" title="US Open definition"><span class="ndv">US Open</span></a> (1968) and <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/wimbledon" title="Wimbledon definition"><span class="ndv">Wimbledon</span></a> (1975). He became captain of the US <a class="Ref" href="https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/the-davis-cup#the_davis_cup_topg_1" title="Davis Cup definition"><span class="ndv">Davis Cup</span></a> team in 1983.</span></span>    <div id="ring-links-box">
